AIR WARLOCK: Elemental mage of wind, storm, and lightning

An elemental mage attuned to air and lightning, commanding winds,
calling storms, and hurling bolts of elemental energy. Air Warlocks
draw PPE from ley lines and the open sky, and are feared wherever
weather and magic intersect on Rifts Earth.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Skills: Lore magic, wilderness survival, meditation, holistic
    medicine, plus elective picks from Technical, Lore, and Physical
    categories.
  Attribute requirements: ME 12.
  Equipment: Light robes or travelling clothes, focus crystal attuned
    to air, spellbook of elemental invocations, and a concealed
    sidearm.
  Credits: 500 credits (standard kit).
  PPE / ISP: Base PPE 35, +8 per level. No starting ISP.

